atom.val:
`iterate n tac` runs `tac` exactly `n` times.
`iterate tac` runs `tac` repeatedly until failure.

`iterate`'s argument is a tactic sequence,
so multiple tactics can be run using `iterate n (tac; tac; )` or
```lean
iterate n
  tac
  tac
  
```
